<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:16:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列-约旦边境的袭击对阿卜杜拉国王构成严重政治威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</link><description>袭击夺走了三名以色列人的生命，随后安曼爆发了支持抗议活动，袭击发生在约旦议会选举前三天。鉴于加沙地带持续的战争和王国的经济困难，反对党可能会挑战国王的政策</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因发布威胁人质母亲的视频而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</link><description>警方逮捕了一名来自以色列北部的男子，据称他发布了一段视频，威胁要袭击已在加沙被关押超过 11 个月的 Matan 的母亲 Einav Zangauker</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队告诉家人，在被谋杀的加沙人质上发现了防御伤痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</link><description>以色列国防军上周取回了人质的尸体，并表示他们在士兵抵达前不久被处决。据一名人质亲属称，家人被告知隧道内场面混乱，人质身上发现有防御伤痕</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</guid></item><item><title>枪、辫子和警惕的眼睛：这位埃塞俄比亚以色列艺术家拒绝陈词滥调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</link><description>雷切尔·安约 (Rachel Anyo) 掌控了自己的叙事，创作出具有挑衅性的作品，直面黑人女性气质、潜在的暴力和社会期望，并大胆拒绝强加给她的谦虚</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡请求法院阻止在即将上映的电影中播放他的审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</link><description>耶路撒冷法院在提交请愿书后不久就驳回了请愿书，距离“比比档案”计划在多伦多电影节首映几个小时</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列袭击了叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的地点，包括化学武器设施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</link><description>叙利亚官方媒体称以色列连夜对哈马附近发动袭击 反对派战争监察员称七人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都会为司法部长对司法系统的痴迷付出代价，甚至可能是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</link><description>以色列最高法院的法官们别无选择，被迫拒绝命令司法部长遵守法律条文，召开一年多没有开会的司法任命委员会，以便它可以根据资历制度选举新的最高法院院长</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 04:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部住宅楼在黎巴嫩火灾后遭受直接袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</link><description>耶路撒冷警方拆除抗议帐篷，暴力驱散要求人质交易的抗议者 ■ 约旦谴责艾伦比十字路口袭击，强调两国解决方案的必要性 ■ 总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡表示，未经他批准，部长们不得进入圣殿山/阿克萨大院，断言不会对网站的状态进行任何更改</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长预计推迟任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</link><description>一位与司法部长亚里夫·莱文关系密切的人士表示，“他不会做一个好孩子，安静地接受裁决”，他指的是最高法院要求他必须任命一位新总统的裁决，“但他也不会违反这一裁决”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</guid></item><item><title>他们为赫什·戈德堡-波林和奥里·达尼诺而战。在湿婆节，他们见到了家人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</link><description>达尼诺和戈德伯格-波林一家上周在相距几英里的地方举行了湿婆礼，但认识并不是人们来到他们家的先决条件。一位曾拜访过这两家公司的人士表示，“我是来安慰自己的，也希望得到一点安慰”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡自己的话暴露了他的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的说法——哈马斯独自阻止了一项协议——证明了他的策略的失败，如果一开始就有策略的话</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 19:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</guid></item><item><title>“这是我的职责”：是什么让这些活动分子来到约旦河谷的一个巴勒斯坦小镇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列定居者以约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦城镇的al-Auja溪流为目标，切断当地人的水源。一群以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在现场游行，决心因剥夺和战争而“圣化生命”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</guid></item><item><title>摩尔多瓦拒绝批准降落后，乌曼飞往哈西德派犹太人的航班可能会被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</link><description>成千上万想要参观布拉茨拉夫拉比·纳赫曼坟墓的持票人已被告知，摩尔多瓦政府拒绝批准布拉茨拉夫·哈西丁飞经基希讷乌机场。正在探索飞往罗马尼亚的替代航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</guid></item><item><title>目击者称以色列军队在没有发生冲突的情况下射杀了美国活动家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</link><description>“我们站着，军队可以看到，只是站在那里什么也不做。什么也没发生。我听到两声枪响，”一位也参加了艾森努尔·埃兹吉·埃吉被杀的示威活动的抗议者说道</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第338天：外国外交官称停战谈判“没有任何进展”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</link><description>约旦人向以色列-约旦边境口岸开火，造成三名以色列人死亡 ■ 熟悉停战谈判的消息人士：“只有当双方都认为有兴趣时才会发生” ■ 以色列安全内阁周日晚间讨论协议 ■ 以色列国防军：向北部发射了 50 枚火箭弹以色列从黎巴嫩出发 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人启程参加停火运动，并在埃及和黎巴嫩停留，但不包括以色列 ■ 战争结束 338 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</guid></item><item><title>Nur Shams 和 Tul Karm 被毁的街道不容置疑。约旦河西岸是战区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-destroyed-streets-in-tul-karm-leave-no-room-for-doubt-the-west-bank-is-a-war-zone/00000191-cd0e-df60-a79b-cd7fe8730000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦居民说，“这是企图将我们连根拔起，他们试图将难民营的居民从我们的家中连根拔起，但我们不会去。”随着以色列军队加强在西岸北部难民营的行动，居民担心该地区将成为新的加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-destroyed-streets-in-tul-karm-leave-no-room-for-doubt-the-west-bank-is-a-war-zone/00000191-cd0e-df60-a79b-cd7fe8730000</guid></item><item><title>“对以色列存在明显的偏见”：10 月 7 日 BBC 加沙战争报道报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/report-accuses-bbc-of-anti-israel-bias-during-war-in-gaza/00000191-d1cb-d214-a393-d5fb39460000</link><description>《每日电讯报》的报道称，“调查结果揭示了 BBC 存在令人深感担忧的偏见模式，并且多次违反其有关公正、公平和确立真相的编辑指南”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/report-accuses-bbc-of-anti-israel-bias-during-war-in-gaza/00000191-d1cb-d214-a393-d5fb39460000</guid></item><item><title>呼吁达成人质协议的被拘留抗议者表示，他们被问及是否得到报酬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/detained-protesters-calling-for-hostage-deal-say-they-were-asked-if-theyre-being-paid/00000191-d1cb-d25e-a1f7-d7cb85260000</link><description>三名被捕的抗议者表示，他们被带到以色列中部的一名情报官员那里，该官员试图获取有关抗议组织者的信息。一名被拘留者说，“他询问资金问题，甚至提到了埃胡德·巴拉克”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/detained-protesters-calling-for-hostage-deal-say-they-were-asked-if-theyre-being-paid/00000191-d1cb-d25e-a1f7-d7cb85260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列海岸发现极度濒危吉他鱼的天然苗圃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</link><description>小黑鳅吉它鱼栖息在马甘迈克尔的砂岩海湾中，直到达到足以勇敢面对公海的临界尺寸</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:34:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争成为威尼斯电影节的焦点，获奖者声援巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦和美国犹太导演都因其电影获奖，直接解决了这一冲突。斯坎达尔·科普蒂说：“我们的电影着眼于道德叙事如何将我们团结在一起......但同时也让我们对他人的痛苦视而不见。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>